description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. Completely non-scripted, all in front of a live audience, broadcast live to members. Today's update is round one of four. This was May's live match, now edited for your enjoyment.
Wrestling Demigod par excellence Ariel X teams up with rookie Bryn Blayne to battle tough veteran Bella Rossi and the rookie Penny Barber. If anyone can stand up to the steamroller that is Ariel X, it is the Annihilator, Bella Rossi. Do not miss this exciting round one!
title: RD 1/4 of May's Live Tag Team Match: Totally non-scripted lesbian wrestling!
